$ CSSStyleDeclaration (interface)
@ CSSStyleDeclaration

A `CSSStyleDeclaration` interface might be obtained from
  • → development/web/browser/object-model/window/getComputedStyle[`window.getComputedStyle()`]
  • `→ development/web/HTML/DOM/API/interfaces-classes/HTMLElement[HTMLElement].style`
  • `→ development/web/browser/object-model/document[document].styleSheets[i].cssRules[j].style`

